cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper discusses a new optimizer called AvaGrad that outperforms SGD and Adam on vision tasks and character-level language modeling. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
